rows.label: qst200206_msg0001
rows.name:
Harghal went back to live with
her family in Alba Margen.

rows.label: qst200206_msg0002
rows.name:
I don't know where she lived exactly,
but her family aren't rich, so maybe
that will point you in the right direction.

rows.label: qst200206_msg0003
rows.name:
If you do find her, let her know
how I'm doing, OK?

rows.label: qst200206_msg0105
rows.name:
She was an incredible dancer -
everyone's darling, Bahn's favorite.

rows.label: qst200206_msg0106
rows.name:
And then she betrayed me and just left!
I couldn't care less about that skank!
